<!DOCTYPE html>
<html style="margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;border: none;">

<head style="margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;border: none;">
    <meta charset="utf-8" style="margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;border: none;">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" style="margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;border: none;">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" style="margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;border: none;">
</head>

<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;color: #313132;">
    <table style="width: 580px;">
        <tr>
            <td style="width: 151px;">
                <img style="width: 151px;" src="https://${host}/static/media/logo-banner.e5eec500e32dc7377862.png">
            </td>
            <td>
                <span id="sds_muncipality_notification" style="overflow: visible;line-height: 30px;text-align: left;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;font-size: 20px;color: rgba(0, 51, 102, 1);letter-spacing: -0.2px;vertical-align: middle;">Site Remediation Services</span>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <table style="width: 580px;">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <hr color="#DBDCDC" size="1px">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p class="info" style="margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 0;overflow: visible;line-height: 24px;text-align: left;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;color: #313132;letter-spacing: 0px;text-decoration: underline;">
                    Submission received – Action may be required to complete your SDS
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p class="info" style="margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-size: 16px;">
                    Thank you for your submission. <br>
                    This message confirms that we have received your Site Disclosure Statement (SDS).
                </p>
                <p class="info" style="margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;">
                    IMPORTANT: Your submission may be incomplete.
                </p>
                <p class="info" style="margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-size: 16px;">
                    If you have not already uploaded a map showing the location and boundaries of your site, please do so immediately. 
                    A separate email will be sent to you with a link to upload the map via BC Box.
                </p>
                <p class="info" style="margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-size: 16px;">
                    Your SDS will not be reviewed until the map has been received. To avoid delays, please complete this step as soon as possible.
                </p>
                <p class="info" style="margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-size: 16px;">
                    <strong>Once the map is uploaded to BC Box:</strong><br>
                    • Your SDS will be reviewed for completeness.<br>
                    • If anything is missing, you will receive an email outlining what needs to be updated and resubmitted.<br>
                    • If your SDS is complete, you will receive a confirmation email with your Site Identification number (Site ID), which you will need for any future applications related to this site.
                </p>
                <p class="info" style="margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-size: 16px;">
                    If you have any questions, please send your enquiry to 
                    <a href="mailto:SiteID@gov.bc.ca" style="color: #1A5A96;text-decoration: underline;">SiteID@gov.bc.ca</a>.
                </p>
                <p class="info" style="margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-size: 16px;">
                    <strong>Learn More About Site Identification in B.C.</strong><br>
                    You can find helpful information about Site Identification, including SDS, here: 
                    <a href="https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/environment/air-land-water/site-remediation/identifying-and-disclosing-sites-that-may-be-contaminated" style="color: #1A5A96;text-decoration: underline;">Identifying and Disclosing Sites</a>
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding-top: 24px;">
                <hr color="#DBDCDC" size="1px">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p class="footer">Have questions or need help? Please email us at:
                    <a class="footer_link" href="mailto:${support}">${support}</a>
                </p>
                <p> BC Public Services will never send an email that asks you to provide, confirm or verify personal, log on or account information.
                    DO NOT reply to this email as it was sent from an unmonitored account.
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>